.H 2 "pathname"
The function requires one or more arguments,
being files names to be replaced with their full path names.
.H 3 "Example"
Relative names are made absolute,
and redundant slashes and dots are removed:
.eB
pwd = [pathname .];
.eE
.H 3 "See Also"
basename,
dirname,
entryname
